assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Needs Well Inc. engages in the IT service business in Japan. It provides NW Security Police, which prevents unauthorized connection; Remote PC array, a remote access solution that contains multiple physical PC cartridges and components for virtual desktops in a single chassis; Resalio Lynx, a USB thin client solution that securely connect to a virtual environment; okta, a cloud-based ID management and integrated authentication service, that manages single sign-on, ID management, access control, etc. on cloud; ESET protect solution, an endpoint security solution; VOTIRO Disarmer, an email or file sanitization solution; Symantec Web Isolation solutions; and MobiControl, a mobile device management. The company also offers SmartWMS, a warehouse management system; IT re-engineering services, an in-house system operation consulting and data linkage system construction; WinActor, a business automation robot; SAP Concur, a cloud system for business trip, expense management, and invoice management cloud system; CONTRACTHUB@absonne, an electronic contract solution; DenHo, an Electronic ledger storage cloud service; Walk Me, a digitization support tool that accelerates corporate DX; zero one sim, a data communication cheap SIM; HotProfile, a business card management and sales tool; 2025 Solution, an DX promotion solution for financial systems; CXoneCloud, a cloud-based contact center platform; robotic call, a call center automatic call receiving system; and WELCOME, a loan web acceptance system. In addition, it provides Work AI service, a business AI service; DX Suite, which instantly digitize any document; Speak Analyzer, an educational AI solution; Es Prophetter, a machine learning on past quotation data and calculates approximate quotation prices; and Chat documents, a chatbot for document search and internal FAQ. Further, the company offers Web performer, a low-code development platform. Needs Well Inc. was incorporated in 1986 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
